0.4.0
=========
 * Support locking when the session becomes inactive (e.g. on VT switch)

0.3.0
=========
 * Support locking when the session is idle
 * Support dynamically reloading the configuration
 * Add a plugin for integrating more closely with Wayfire

0.2.0
=========
Support using a config file

0.1.0
=========
Initial release
